micro is a simple blogging application based on our very own micro theme for mephisto.  as blogware goes, micro is pretty simple - no themes, no plugins, no user accounts, no asset management, just pure post-it and share it goodness. inspired by the more robust mephisto blogging system, and by bloggers everywhere, micro is powered by ruby, rails, jquery, haml and textile. enjoy.

required gems:
haml
redcloth